			MX8MN_IOMUXC_SD1_DATA3_USDHC1_DATA3		0x156
			MX8MN_IOMUXC_SD1_DATA4_USDHC1_DATA4		0x156
			MX8MN_IOMUXC_SD1_DATA5_USDHC1_DATA5		0x156
